Bryan Street, Owenton, KY 40359 Office Hours are 8:00 a.m. to 4:30 p.m., Monday through Friday, 33999=Copyright © 2015, 20171=Michael and Stacey Miller are excited to announce the birth of their daughter, Brenna Raye. She arrived at 7:45 p.m. on Feb. 5, 2013. She weighed 7 pounds, 7 ounces and was 21 inches long. Her proud grandparents are Billy and June Prather, Roxanne and Owen Bennett and George and Donna Miller, all of Owenton; and her great-grandfather is Herbert Prather of Owenton.  }
